1
00:00:08,015 --> 00:00:18,031
♪

2
00:00:18,064 --> 00:00:28,114
♪

3
00:00:28,114 --> 00:00:38,129
♪

4
00:01:38,290 --> 00:01:46,068
♪

5
00:01:57,319 --> 00:01:59,088
{\an1}(Sasuke)
Kakashi?

6
00:01:59,121 --> 00:02:01,024
{\an1}You're not usually here first.

7
00:02:01,058 --> 00:02:03,961
Well, it happens
once in a while...

8
00:02:03,995 --> 00:02:08,936
{\an1}So what's going on? Why
did you summon us here?

9
00:02:08,969 --> 00:02:12,942
<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Sasuke...! You've grown up...</i>

10
00:02:22,925 --> 00:02:25,895
{\an1}It's been a long time Sasuke.

11
00:02:25,929 --> 00:02:28,400
{\an1}Itachi Uchiha

12
00:02:28,433 --> 00:02:33,843
{\an1}I hope you're ready... to die!

13
00:02:33,875 --> 00:02:36,879
{\an1}Well The Sharingan.

14
00:02:36,912 --> 00:02:39,484
{\an1}...And he looks an
awful lot like <i>you</i> .

15
00:02:39,518 --> 00:02:41,387
{\an1}...Itachi, who <i>is</i> this kid?

16
00:02:41,420 --> 00:02:43,056
He's my younger brother.

17
00:02:43,089 --> 00:02:46,863
So you've awakened
your Sharingan.

18
00:02:46,895 --> 00:02:51,034
<i>Of course... you</i>
<i>would've already</i>

19
00:02:51,068 --> 00:02:53,906
{\an1}It's just as you said, brother

20
00:02:53,939 --> 00:02:57,111
{\an1}I've fostered my hatred
all this time

21
00:02:57,145 --> 00:03:01,050
{\an1}I've lived my life all in
pursuit of one single purpose

22
00:03:01,084 --> 00:03:03,855
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>How strong have you become?</i>

23
00:03:03,889 --> 00:03:06,125
To kill you

24
00:03:06,159 --> 00:03:08,128
It ends here!

25
00:03:08,162 --> 00:03:10,298
Chidori?

26
00:03:10,331 --> 00:03:17,342
{\an1}[attack cry] Die!!!

27
00:03:17,376 --> 00:03:21,382
{\an1}<i>(Itachi Thinking)</i>
<i>I see.  It was Kakashi, huh? </i>

28
00:03:21,416 --> 00:03:23,786
[bone snap]
[crying in pain]

29
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:28,159
{\an1}Sasuke!! All right, that's it!

30
00:03:30,162 --> 00:03:31,431
{\an1}Ninja art! Summo-

31
00:03:31,465 --> 00:03:33,134
Too slow!

32
00:03:42,348 --> 00:03:44,351
<i>(Itachi)</i>
<i>Master Jiraiya</i>

33
00:03:44,384 --> 00:03:45,787
{\an1}I know he's the one
you're really after.

34
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:51,262
{\an1}You're right. Naruto is the
prize that the Akatsuki are
after...

35
00:03:51,295 --> 00:03:53,599
{\an1}...And we will have him.

36
00:03:53,633 --> 00:03:56,135
{\an1}No way you're getting Naruto.

37
00:03:56,169 --> 00:03:59,407
{\an1}We'll see about that.

38
00:03:59,442 --> 00:04:02,881
{\an1}Actually, this is all
very convenient...

39
00:04:02,914 --> 00:04:05,083
{\an1}I can eliminate you
both at the same time.

40
00:04:05,116 --> 00:04:08,421
Stay out of this!

41
00:04:08,456 --> 00:04:16,100
{\an1}...The only one... who's going
to eliminate him... is me!

42
00:04:16,133 --> 00:04:18,571
{\an1}You don't interest
me at the moment.

43
00:04:18,604 --> 00:04:21,843
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Not yet, Sasuke...</i>

44
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:24,246
[grunts]

45
00:04:25,282 --> 00:04:27,251
{\an1}<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Sasuke no! </i>

46
00:04:27,285 --> 00:04:28,587
{\an1}Why you lousy!

47
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:32,258
{\an1}No Naruto! Don't butt in,
mind your own business!

48
00:04:32,292 --> 00:04:34,094
[gasp]

49
00:04:34,128 --> 00:04:36,165
Just back off! This
fight is mine!

50
00:04:36,198 --> 00:04:38,602
[grunt]

51
00:04:38,635 --> 00:04:41,306
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>That's right!</i>

52
00:04:41,340 --> 00:04:44,011
And now, finally--!

53
00:04:44,045 --> 00:04:47,649
[grunts]

54
00:04:49,419 --> 00:04:50,588
{\an1}<i>(Itachi Thinking)</i>
<i>You don't have enough...</i>

55
00:04:50,621 --> 00:04:53,124
[coughs blood]

56
00:04:55,662 --> 00:05:00,670
{\an1}<i>(Itachi Thinking)</i>
<i>Forgive me, Sasuke!  Forgive me!</i>

57
00:05:00,704 --> 00:05:04,977
{\an1}You show him no mercy.

58
00:05:12,488 --> 00:05:17,496
<i>Hate me more...</i>

59
00:05:18,664 --> 00:05:21,469
{\an1}<i>You're weak, Sasuke.</i>

60
00:05:21,502 --> 00:05:28,480
{\an1}<i>And for the next twenty-four</i>
<i>hours... Relive that day...</i>

61
00:05:30,116 --> 00:05:33,054
{\an1}You're using Tsukuyomi on
your younger brother?

62
00:05:33,087 --> 00:05:37,326
{\an1}That's it! I'm through
standing around!

63
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:44,437
[gasp]

64
00:05:47,710 --> 00:05:50,781
{\an1}You're still too weak...

65
00:05:50,814 --> 00:05:55,555
{\an1}You just don't have enough hate.

66
00:05:55,588 --> 00:05:57,158
Kisame, come.

67
00:05:58,060 --> 00:05:59,260
Stop! [grunt]

68
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:06,405
{\an1}Why did we have to retreat?
You could've won that fight.

69
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:09,143
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Sasuke</i>

70
00:06:09,177 --> 00:06:13,616
{\an7}<i>Even though Lord Third</i>
<i>is dead, you still have people</i>
<i>who will protect you </i>

71
00:06:13,650 --> 00:06:17,756
{\an7}<i>I'll be waiting, Sasuke.</i>

72
00:06:22,864 --> 00:06:25,267
{\an1}Why are you so obsessed
with my brother?!

73
00:06:25,301 --> 00:06:28,238
{\an1}He's just a rogue
ninja.

74
00:06:28,271 --> 00:06:34,081
{\an4}It's true that we may not be
blood, but he's more of a
brother to me than you ever were
to him.

75
00:06:36,518 --> 00:06:42,094
{\an1}I know that you've been trying
to take Sasuke back to the
Hidden Leaf Village.

76
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:45,867
{\an1}However, what if it doesn't go
the way you want it to?

77
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:48,637
{\an1}I'll do anything
to make it happen.

78
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:53,277
{\an1}You just said you consider
Sasuke... to be like a
brother to you.

79
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:56,717
{\an1}What if Sasuke were to attack
the Hidden Leaf Village?

80
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,820
{\an1}What would you do then?

81
00:06:59,654 --> 00:07:03,795
{\an1}Why would-? No, there's just no
way that Sasuke would ever do
something like that!

82
00:07:03,828 --> 00:07:06,832
{\an1}Sasuke is still a blank canvas.

83
00:07:06,865 --> 00:07:09,804
{\an1}He can easily be dyed
into any color.

84
00:07:09,837 --> 00:07:13,576
{\an1}If he resists... would you
be able to stop him?

85
00:07:16,413 --> 00:07:18,818
{\an1}Or even kill him if need be?

86
00:07:18,851 --> 00:07:20,220
[gasp]

87
00:07:21,621 --> 00:07:24,226
{\an1}Could you weigh Sasuke against
the Hidden Leaf on a set of
scales?

88
00:07:24,259 --> 00:07:26,429
{\an1}I would defend the Village!

89
00:07:26,462 --> 00:07:29,333
{\an1}And I'd find a way to stop
Sasuke without killing him!

90
00:07:29,366 --> 00:07:31,704
{\an1}You're such a child

91
00:07:31,737 --> 00:07:34,275
{\an1}All your tales are nothing
but mere fantasies

92
00:07:34,309 --> 00:07:38,582
{\an1}Shinobi must be capable of
making very harsh decisions

93
00:07:38,615 --> 00:07:42,487
{\an1}Someone else once tried to
tell me this same thing.

94
00:07:42,521 --> 00:07:44,791
{\an1}But for me, there is no choice.

95
00:07:44,824 --> 00:07:47,662
{\an1}I gave my word and
I'll never back down

96
00:07:47,696 --> 00:07:50,466
{\an1}That will always
be my Ninja Way!

97
00:07:50,499 --> 00:07:53,204
I see.

98
00:07:54,472 --> 00:07:57,377
He's here.

99
00:07:57,410 --> 00:08:02,986
{\an1}How much can you see? With
those Sharingan of yours?

100
00:08:03,019 --> 00:08:09,496
{\an1}What I'm seeing right now,
Itachi... is you dead at my feet!

101
00:08:09,529 --> 00:08:13,535
{\an1}You see me dead, do you?

102
00:08:15,739 --> 00:08:18,777
Well, then...

103
00:08:21,315 --> 00:08:23,285
{\an1}Go on, make it happen.

104
00:08:32,332 --> 00:08:37,506
[groaning]

105
00:08:37,539 --> 00:08:39,810
[gasp]

106
00:08:59,908 --> 00:09:04,983
{\an1}Forgive me, Sasuke
But this is the end.

107
00:09:28,152 --> 00:09:31,491
{\an1}You don't ever have
to forgive me.

108
00:09:37,433 --> 00:09:41,538
{\an1}No matter what, I
will love you always.

109
00:09:58,031 --> 00:09:59,666
{\an1}<i>(Sasuke Thinking)</i>
<i>I...</i>

110
00:10:05,042 --> 00:10:10,984
{\an1}<i>I've made up my</i>
<i>mind, Big Brother</i>

111
00:10:32,751 --> 00:10:36,458
{\an1}All that's left... is them.

112
00:10:42,267 --> 00:10:46,473
{\an1}So it really didn't
let the light through

113
00:10:46,507 --> 00:10:49,711
Finally.

114
00:10:49,744 --> 00:10:53,750
{\an1}Looks like that Zetsu guy wasn't
affected by it at all...

115
00:10:53,783 --> 00:10:57,656
{\an1}Sasuke! We gotta wake them all
up from the genjutsu. But how?

116
00:10:57,689 --> 00:11:01,129
{\an1}Rinnegan genjutsu can be dealt
with using Rinnegan.

117
00:11:01,163 --> 00:11:02,932
Probably...

118
00:11:02,965 --> 00:11:05,903
Which means Sasuke's
left eye is necessary...

119
00:11:05,936 --> 00:11:11,878
{\an1}I won't let that happen. All
that's left is to get rid of
you guys...

120
00:11:11,913 --> 00:11:16,819
{\an1}Which I, the savior of
the world shall do.

121
00:11:16,853 --> 00:11:20,192
Madara!

122
00:11:29,906 --> 00:11:34,781
{\an1}That eye on his forehead!

123
00:11:34,814 --> 00:11:39,121
{\an1}Be careful. We're
surrounded on all sides
by four of his Shadows.

124
00:11:39,155 --> 00:11:40,991
Yeah, I know that!

125
00:11:41,024 --> 00:11:43,795
{\an1}I won't let you do
anything else.

126
00:11:43,828 --> 00:11:46,933
{\an1}I just severed the Karmic
Cycle of this world.

127
00:11:46,967 --> 00:11:54,178
{\an1}I have freed humankind from
their suffering, pain, and
futility.

128
00:11:54,211 --> 00:11:57,250
{\an1}But all this... It's
all just a lie!

129
00:11:57,283 --> 00:12:01,889
{\an1}Right now... you're the one
interfering with everyone's
happiness,  Naruto.

130
00:12:01,923 --> 00:12:03,125
{\an1}[gasp]

131
00:12:03,158 --> 00:12:07,198
{\an1}Look! All the fighting among
shinobi has come to an end now!

132
00:12:07,231 --> 00:12:13,742
{\an1}<i>I've transformed hell into</i>
<i>heaven.  I've finally corrected</i>
<i>Hashirama's mistake.</i>

133
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:16,713
{\an1}What are you talking about?
What do you mean, his "mistake?"

134
00:12:16,747 --> 00:12:22,789
{\an1}You Hidden Leaf shinobi may not
want to admit it,... but
Hashirama ultimately failed.

135
00:12:22,822 --> 00:12:26,128
{\an1}He did not reform
the Shinobi World.

136
00:12:26,161 --> 00:12:29,933
{\an1}In the beginning, both Hashirama
and I had the same ambitions.

137
00:12:29,967 --> 00:12:32,904
{\an1}And we worked together
to try to achieve them.

138
00:12:32,937 --> 00:12:37,045
{\an1}<i>We tried to change the</i>
<i>shinobi world,</i>

139
00:12:37,078 --> 00:12:43,054
{\an1}<i>the abominable system that sent</i>
<i>barely grown children out to</i>
<i>fight in wars.</i>

140
00:12:45,924 --> 00:12:49,163
{\an1}<i>The two of us founded the</i>
<i>first shinobi village.</i>

141
00:12:49,196 --> 00:12:52,401
{\an1}<i>But even that did not</i>
<i>result in true peace.</i>

142
00:12:52,436 --> 00:12:56,040
{\an1}<i>People simply aren't able to</i>
<i>show each other their true</i>
<i>feelings.</i>

143
00:12:56,074 --> 00:13:01,683
{\an1}<i>Fear, suspicion, resentment...</i>
<i>They never subside.</i>

144
00:13:02,117 --> 00:13:05,823
{\an1}<i>My opinions and concerns</i>
<i>were pushed aside,</i>

145
00:13:05,855 --> 00:13:11,030
{\an1}<i>and the Shinobi World moved</i>
<i>forward in accordance with</i>
<i>Hashirama's vision.</i>

146
00:13:11,063 --> 00:13:13,434
{\an1}<i>And what happened because of it?</i>

147
00:13:13,468 --> 00:13:16,473
{\an1}<i>Well, the fighting among</i>
<i>shinobi hasn't stopped.</i>

148
00:13:16,506 --> 00:13:22,750
{\an1}<i>Instead, establishing ninja</i>
<i>villages led to an increase in</i>
<i>military build-up...</i>

149
00:13:22,783 --> 00:13:28,090
{\an1}<i>...resulting in skirmishes that</i>
<i>turned into great wars with</i>
<i>countless lives lost.</i>

150
00:13:28,124 --> 00:13:30,927
{\an1}<i>There was the First</i>
<i>Great Ninja War</i>

151
00:13:30,961 --> 00:13:35,034
{\an1}<i>The Second Great Ninja War</i>

152
00:13:35,068 --> 00:13:39,842
{\an1}<i>The Third Great Ninja War</i>

153
00:13:39,876 --> 00:13:45,250
{\an1}<i>The fighting never stopped.</i>
<i>That's the Shinobi World</i>
<i>Hashirama created.</i>

154
00:13:45,284 --> 00:13:52,429
{\an1}I will admit, I was the one
responsible for triggering this
Fourth Great Ninja War

155
00:13:52,462 --> 00:13:55,433
{\an1}That's right! Because
of you, so many died!

156
00:13:55,466 --> 00:14:00,240
{\an1}I also proposed that the
Tailed Beasts be handed
over peacefully.

157
00:14:00,274 --> 00:14:05,080
{\an1}Now everyone's inside the Divine
Tree, all dreaming idyllic
dreams.

158
00:14:05,114 --> 00:14:09,789
{\an1}And all of them are now
enjoying their ideal worlds.

159
00:14:09,823 --> 00:14:12,025
{\an1}This is your idea
of a perfect world?

160
00:14:12,058 --> 00:14:15,464
{\an1}You're way off. You're
only deceiving people.

161
00:14:15,497 --> 00:14:24,846
{\an4}All that I'm seeking to do is to
become the savior that ends the
long history of fighting amongst
shinobi.

162
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,915
{\an1}It's time you woke up.

163
00:14:26,949 --> 00:14:29,452
{\an1}...It's all over.

164
00:14:30,855 --> 00:14:32,557
{\an1}Huh?

165
00:14:35,863 --> 00:14:40,069
(Black Zetsu)
Wrong, Madara. You
are not the savior.

166
00:14:40,102 --> 00:14:43,374
{\an1}Nor is this the end of things.

167
00:14:46,946 --> 00:14:50,519
{\an1}I can't move!

168
00:14:50,552 --> 00:14:52,287
{\an1}What's going on?!

169
00:14:52,321 --> 00:15:00,300
{\an1}How can you say that you, unlike
Obito, are able to completely
take advantage of others?

170
00:15:00,333 --> 00:15:05,408
{\an1}Isn't it presumptuous to think
that you alone are different?

171
00:15:05,441 --> 00:15:11,384
{\an1}My dear Madara,... you have also
been caught inside a phantom
dream

172
00:15:11,417 --> 00:15:16,158
{\an1}...a dream that I concocted.

173
00:15:16,191 --> 00:15:20,464
{\an1}Inside a dream...? What are you
talking about, Black Zetsu?

174
00:15:20,498 --> 00:15:23,938
{\an1}I was the one who created
you in the first place!

175
00:15:23,971 --> 00:15:28,544
{\an1}You are nothing more than
my will made incarnate!

176
00:15:28,578 --> 00:15:34,620
{\an1}Wrong again... My
will is... Kaguya's!

177
00:15:34,653 --> 00:15:37,992
{\an1}What the hell is going on now?!

178
00:15:38,025 --> 00:15:40,262
{\an1}They're having a
falling out, now?!

179
00:15:40,295 --> 00:15:43,935
{\an1}No, that isn't it. He
just mentioned Kaguya.

180
00:15:43,969 --> 00:15:44,569
Kaguya?

181
00:15:44,603 --> 00:15:46,038
{\an1}And what's that?!

182
00:15:46,072 --> 00:15:49,176
{\an1}The one the Sage of Six
Paths mentioned.

183
00:15:49,209 --> 00:15:53,083
{\an1}<i>(Sage of Six Paths)</i>
<i>The current Madara is a</i>
<i>perfect example.</i>

184
00:15:53,148 --> 00:15:55,418
{\an1}<i>. He's become just</i>
<i>like my mother...</i>

185
00:15:55,452 --> 00:15:58,557
{\an1}<i>he's obtained Ten Tails' power</i>
<i>and is getting close to me.</i>

186
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:02,731
{\an1}<i>And he's trying to obtain even</i>
<i>my mother Kaguya's power.</i>

187
00:16:02,764 --> 00:16:06,970
{\an1}<i>However, my mother's power bred</i>
<i>arrogance within her.  </i>

188
00:16:07,004 --> 00:16:10,342
{\an1}<i>And mankind began to dread the</i>
<i>existence of that power.</i>

189
00:16:10,376 --> 00:16:13,648
No way

190
00:16:17,453 --> 00:16:19,188
What's that?!

191
00:16:23,429 --> 00:16:26,467
Their chakra...
It's being absorbed?

192
00:16:26,501 --> 00:16:31,142
{\an1}[agonizing scream]

193
00:16:31,174 --> 00:16:32,076
[gasp]

194
00:16:36,382 --> 00:16:41,457
{\an1}Whoa, what the hell is happening
with him?! That chakra's
incredible!

195
00:16:41,490 --> 00:16:45,697
{\an1}All of Madara's Shadows have
disappeared!  Something's going
on!

196
00:16:47,299 --> 00:16:51,439
<i>[cracking]</i>

197
00:16:51,472 --> 00:16:53,543
(Sasuke)
It's chakra!

198
00:16:53,576 --> 00:16:58,416
<i>[rushing wind]</i>

199
00:17:00,519 --> 00:17:03,224
[chuckling]

200
00:17:03,257 --> 00:17:09,467
{\an1}Is he absorbing all this chakra
that's erupting from the ground?

201
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:13,372
{\an1}Where did all of this thick,
dark chakra come from?!

202
00:17:13,406 --> 00:17:18,081
{\an1}It's probably from all those
trapped in the Infinite
Tsukuyomi!

203
00:17:18,115 --> 00:17:19,750
[screams]

204
00:17:19,783 --> 00:17:22,286
{\an1}This is really bad, Sasuke!

205
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:25,425
{\an1}This chakra's way stronger
than even Ten Tails'!

206
00:17:25,458 --> 00:17:27,629
{\an1}Stop them before they move!

207
00:17:31,267 --> 00:17:33,138
Go, Naruto!

208
00:17:33,171 --> 00:17:37,677
{\an1}You mean we gotta stop 'em while
they're still swelling up,
right?

209
00:17:42,317 --> 00:17:43,254
huh?

210
00:17:44,755 --> 00:17:47,693
[grunts]

211
00:17:47,727 --> 00:17:51,533
<i>(Black Zetsu)</i>
<i>You're like two moths</i>
<i>flying into the flame!</i>

212
00:17:51,566 --> 00:17:55,539
{\an1}<i>I'm gonna absorb the chakra</i>
<i>from the both of you, too.</i>

213
00:17:55,572 --> 00:17:56,808
{\an1}Damn it!

214
00:17:56,841 --> 00:17:57,875
{\an1}[determined grunts]

215
00:17:57,909 --> 00:17:59,812
No, Sakura!

216
00:17:59,845 --> 00:18:01,447
{\an1}But, Sensei...!

217
00:18:01,481 --> 00:18:05,188
{\an1}Unless you have a plan,
it'll be wasted.

218
00:18:05,221 --> 00:18:07,691
{\an1}Aw, no way! Come
on! I can't move!

219
00:18:07,724 --> 00:18:11,396
{\an1}Sasuke, if we aren't able
to stop this guy soon...
then he's gonna drain

220
00:18:11,429 --> 00:18:15,269
{\an1}everyone else's chakra
before he gets ours, and
all of them will die!

221
00:18:15,303 --> 00:18:16,537
[grunt]

222
00:18:16,571 --> 00:18:20,211
{\an1}Don't worry. No one
is going to die.

223
00:18:20,244 --> 00:18:26,820
{\an1}Even when Kaguya previously cast
the Infinite Tsukuyomi upon the
populace,

224
00:18:26,854 --> 00:18:30,459
{\an1}she preserved those
people alive...

225
00:18:30,492 --> 00:18:34,498
{\an1}...in order to form them
into her soldiers.

226
00:18:34,532 --> 00:18:37,737
{\an1}To form them...? And
what does that mean?!

227
00:18:37,770 --> 00:18:41,476
{\an1}[laugh] You seem to be
denser than Itachi.

228
00:18:41,509 --> 00:18:44,815
{\an1}Can you use ordinary
people in combat?

229
00:18:44,848 --> 00:18:45,884
[grunt]

230
00:18:45,917 --> 00:18:46,885
{\an1}[gasp]

231
00:18:46,919 --> 00:18:48,355
No way...

232
00:18:48,387 --> 00:18:51,459
{\an1}They're turned into White Zetsu.

233
00:18:51,492 --> 00:18:56,800
{\an1}<i>What's left of those who were</i>
<i>under the previous Infinite</i>
<i>Tsukuyomi... </i>

234
00:18:56,834 --> 00:18:59,704
{\an1}<i>That's what White</i>
<i>Zetsu are.</i>

235
00:18:59,738 --> 00:19:05,014
{\an1}<i>They've become transformed,</i>
<i>slowly, over time.</i>

236
00:19:05,047 --> 00:19:08,319
{\an1}Are you telling us that everyone
is gonna end up as those white
Zetsu?!

237
00:19:08,352 --> 00:19:11,757
{\an1}What are you talking about?!
That can't be, Black Zetsu!

238
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:16,364
{\an1}The Infinite Tsukuyomi
is a jutsu belonging to
the Uchiha Clan!

239
00:19:16,398 --> 00:19:19,435
{\an1}It's one that brings eternal
peace to the shinobi world.

240
00:19:19,468 --> 00:19:22,707
{\an1}And on what do you base
that assumption on?

241
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:27,815
{\an1}Anyone who's able can read it.
It was carved into the Uchiha
stone tablet...

242
00:19:27,848 --> 00:19:30,887
{\an1}...by the Sage of the Six Paths!

243
00:19:35,962 --> 00:19:41,870
{\an1}<i>My dear Madara, I have been</i>
<i>around for eons longer than you.</i>

244
00:19:41,904 --> 00:19:50,550
{\an1}<i>Since finding the stone tablet</i>
<i>left by Hagoromo, I've had quite</i>
<i>some time to make "revisions."</i>

245
00:19:50,583 --> 00:19:52,787
{\an1}What?!  Revisions?!

246
00:19:52,821 --> 00:19:57,862
{\an1}<i>The Infinite Tsukuyomi isn't a</i>
<i>jutsu to create peaceful dreams.</i>

247
00:19:57,895 --> 00:20:03,337
{\an1}<i>It's a jutsu to gather enormous</i>
<i>amounts of chakra from its</i>
<i>captives.</i>

248
00:20:03,371 --> 00:20:05,374
{\an1}For what purpose?

249
00:20:05,407 --> 00:20:08,946
{\an1}<i>For the exact purpose</i>
<i>you just enacted.</i>

250
00:20:08,979 --> 00:20:13,920
{\an1}<i>All according to my will.</i>
<i>Or rather, Kaguya's.</i>

251
00:20:13,954 --> 00:20:17,058
{\an1}No, never! For that-?!

252
00:20:17,091 --> 00:20:24,470
{\an1}<i>Just as you used Obito as a</i>
<i>pawn, you, too, were merely</i>
<i>a pawn.</i>

253
00:20:24,504 --> 00:20:25,772
{\an1}[gasp]

254
00:20:29,844 --> 00:20:32,449
{\an1}Hey, look! He's getting bigger!

255
00:20:32,482 --> 00:20:36,121
{\an1}His body can't tolerate the
amount of chakra that he's
taking in!

256
00:20:36,155 --> 00:20:38,391
{\an1}At this rate, he'll explode!

257
00:20:38,426 --> 00:20:42,432
{\an1}Why?  Why did this happen?!

258
00:20:42,898 --> 00:20:47,906
{\an1}Hashirama Where
did I go wrong?

259
00:20:51,878 --> 00:20:53,382
{\an1}He's shrinking?!

260
00:20:57,521 --> 00:20:58,956
Obito!

261
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:12,744
[gasps]

262
00:21:12,778 --> 00:21:16,016
{\an1}Isn't she the one Super
Gramps mentioned

263
00:21:16,050 --> 00:21:20,557
{\an1}Kaguya Otsutsuki!

264
00:21:28,069 --> 00:21:38,084
♪

265
00:21:38,117 --> 00:21:48,167
♪

266
00:21:48,167 --> 00:21:58,182
♪

267
00:22:57,941 --> 00:23:03,082
<i>(Sakura)</i>
<i>Who is she?  Why'd Madara</i>
<i>suddenly become her?</i>

268
00:23:03,116 --> 00:23:06,656
<i>(Sasuke)</i>
<i>This chakra... It's far</i>
<i>greater than Madara's!</i>

269
00:23:06,689 --> 00:23:08,625
{\an1}<i>I can't believe such</i>
<i>a person existed!</i>

270
00:23:08,659 --> 00:23:12,363
{\an1}<i>Hagoromo knew she'd appear,</i>
<i>that's why he gave us...</i>

271
00:23:12,397 --> 00:23:15,235
<i>(Kakashi)</i>
<i>Sakura, don't make any</i>
<i>careless moves right now.</i>

272
00:23:15,268 --> 00:23:21,110
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Next time on Naruto Shippuden:</i>
<i>"She of the Beginning."</i>

273
00:23:21,144 --> 00:23:22,980
<i>(Kakashi)</i>
<i>What are your intentions?!</i>

274
00:23:27,186 --> 00:23:35,966
♪

